<li>
Work with the CEO to build pitch books and develop presentations for investors.</li>
<li>
Assess company business issues, data challenges, strengths and weaknesses and suggest areas of improvement.</li>
<li>
Provide data-driven insights to guide the company&#39;s evolution, better fulfill our mission, and improve the overall customer experience.</li>
